Cowhead Pure Milk is made from 100% pure fresh milk. It is 100% antibiotic-free, hormone-free, non-GMO and most importantly, free-range and grass-fed.
Cowhead Pure Milk is:
•100% pure fresh milk
•Antibiotic-free
•Hormone-free
•Non-GMO
•Free-range and grass-fed
Type of Milk: Regular milk
Ideal for: Health-conscious individuals, growing children, active adults, and anyone seeking a wholesome, natural milk option.
Ingredients: 100% Natural Fresh Cow's Milk.
Allergen Information: Contains milk.
Storage Instructions: Store in a cool, dry place before opening. Once opened, keep refrigerated at +6°C maximum and consume within 3 days. ______________________________________________________________________________
